issue_body:
The issue can be reproduced using the following commands:

```
PUT /_synonyms/dummy-synonyms_set
{
  "synonyms_set": [
    {
      "id": "1",
      "synonyms": "dummy"
    }
  ]
}

PUT /synonyms_test
{
  "settings": {
    "analysis": {
      "filter": {
        "synonyms": {
          "type": "synonym_graph",
          "updateable": true,
          "synonyms_set": "dummy-synonyms_set"
        }
      },
      "analyzer": {
        "dummy": {
          "type": "custom",
          "tokenizer": "standard",
          "filter": ["synonyms"]
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "mappings": {
    "properties": {
      "title": {
        "type": "search_as_you_type",
        "search_analyzer": "dummy"
      }
    }
  }
}


POST /synonyms_test/_doc/1
{
  "title": "synonyms test"
}

GET /synonyms_test/_search?error_trace=true
{
  "query": {
    "multi_match": {
      "query": "dummy",
      "fields": ["title", "title._2gram"]
    }
  }
}
```

And it fails with the following trace:

```
java.lang.ClassCastException: class org.elasticsearch.index.mapper.extras.SearchAsYouTypeFieldMapper$SearchAsYouTypeAnalyzer cannot be cast to class org.elasticsearch.index.analysis.ReloadableCustomAnalyzer (org.elasticsearch.index.mapper.extras.SearchAsYouTypeFieldMapper$SearchAsYouTypeAnalyzer is in module org.elasticsearch.mapper.extras@9.5.0-SNAPSHOT of loader jdk.internal.loader.Loader @73633230; org.elasticsearch.index.analysis.ReloadableCustomAnalyzer is in module org.elasticsearch.server@9.5.0-SNAPSHOT of loader 'app')
	at org.elasticsearch.server@9.5.0-SNAPSHOT/org.elasticsearch.index.analysis.ReloadableCustomAnalyzer$1.getReusableComponents(ReloadableCustomAnalyzer.java:45)
	at org.apache.lucene.core@10.4.0/org.apache.lucene.analysis.DelegatingAnalyzerWrapper$DelegatingReuseStrategy.getReusableComponents(DelegatingAnalyzerWrapper.java:84)
	at org.apache.lucene.core@10.4.0/org.apache.lucene.analysis.Analyzer.tokenStream(Analyzer.java:184)
	at org.elasticsearch.server@9.5.0-SNAPSHOT/org.elasticsearch.index.search.MatchQueryParser$MatchQueryBuilder.createQuery(MatchQueryParser.java:459)
	at org.elasticsearch.server@9.5.0-SNAPSHOT/org.elasticsearch.index.search.MatchQueryParser$MatchQueryBuilder.createFieldQuery(MatchQueryParser.java:348)
	at org.apache.lucene.core@10.4.0/org.apache.lucene.util.QueryBuilder.createBooleanQuery(QueryBuilder.java:108)
	at org.elasticsearch.server@9.5.0-SNAPSHOT/org.elasticsearch.index.search.MatchQueryParser.parse(MatchQueryParser.java:276)
	at org.elasticsearch.server@9.5.0-SNAPSHOT/org.elasticsearch.index.search.MultiMatchQueryParser.buildFieldQueries(MultiMatchQueryParser.java:97)
	at org.elasticsearch.server@9.5.0-SNAPSHOT/org.elasticsearch.index.search.MultiMatchQueryParser.parse(MultiMatchQueryParser.java:63)
	at org.elasticsearch.server@9.5.0-SNAPSHOT/org.elasticsearch.index.query.MultiMatchQueryBuilder.doToQuery
```

Thei ssue is that the search as you type field mapper wraps the ReloadableCustomAnalyzer with a  SearchAsYouTypeAnalyzer.
